Painkiller Already, LLC is a weekly podcast featuring hosts: WoodysGamertag, FPS Kyle and Murka. Commonly referred to as PKA, the podcast has been steam-rolling through the airwaves since early 2010. PKA discusses current events, news, relives comedic stories and gives their perspective on life while throwing in their comedic twist to all discussions
